predictions.article: US farmers face higher costs, fewer markets from tariffs
predictions.prediction: The imposition of tariffs will lead to a decrease in U.S. agricultural exports to China by at least 10% within the next month.

predictions.article: China hits U.S. agriculture, says it won't be bullied by fresh Trump tariffs
predictions.prediction: The retaliatory tariffs by China will cause a drop in U.S. soybean prices by at least 5% within the next two weeks.
